# NDNC Automation API Configuration

# For local use (default):
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# For network deployment (same WiFi/LAN):
# Replace YOUR_IP with your machine's local IP address
# Example: VITE_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:5000
# VITE_API_URL=http://YOUR_IP:5000

# For remote access (using ngrok):
# Example: VITE_API_URL=https://abc123.ngrok.io
# VITE_API_URL=https://YOUR_NGROK_URL

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Uncomment and set the appropriate VITE_API_URL
# 3. Run 'npm run build' to rebuild with new settings
# 4. Commit and push to deploy to GitHub Pages

